title: The Deep Dive Presents: Full Release with Samantha Bee
description:
Deep Divers we want to share a short clip from a podcast we are loving, it's called Full Release with Samantha Bee. In this clip Sam talks with Jonathan Van Ness about where they do their best thinking and the importance of self care. To listen to this full episode and other great guest interviews with Samantha Bee, follow the Full Release feed wherever you get your podcasts!


 

https://www.earwolf.com/show/full-release-with-samantha-bee/
